      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771651175,
      "updated": 1771651175
    },
    {
      "id": "699943ff00000000008e8445",
      "text": "[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652095,
      "updated": 1771652095
    },
    {
      "id": "699943f100000000008e843f",
      "text": " [& [https://gyazo.com/a58958184e5223de0733792874a17c80]]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652082,
      "updated": 1771652083
    },
    {
      "id": "699943f200000000008e8440",
      "text": " \t🍌に「さわやか」にしてもらったら非常に[キショ]くなった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652083,
      "updated": 1771652083
    },
    {
      "id": "699943f200000000008e8441",
      "text": " \tあまりにキショいのでボカしとこ。",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652083,
      "updated": 1771652083
    },
    {
      "id": "699943f200000000008e8442",
      "text": " \t目無駄にキラッキラで草[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652083,
      "updated": 1771652083
    },
    {
      "id": "699943f200000000008e8443",
      "text": " \t　クチバシと対比するとなお目立つ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652083,
      "updated": 1771652083
    },
    {
      "id": "69994525000000000059ad03",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652389,
      "updated": 1771652391
    },
    {
      "id": "69994514000000000059acff",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652372,
      "updated": 1771652375
    },
    {
      "id": "69994517000000000059ad01",
      "text": " さわやかなアイコン、アイコンでは近づけたので服が見えないが、なぜか[クオリアさん]みたいな服着ていた",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652375,
      "updated": 1771652375
    },
    {
      "id": "69994517000000000059ad02",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/bb4e0f7f734ef7201bde36b95a360e02]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652375,
      "updated": 1771652375
    },
    {
      "id": "69994515000000000059ad00",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652374,
      "updated": 1771652374
    },
    {
      "id": "699943f300000000008e8444",
      "text": "[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652083,
      "updated": 1771652337
    },
    {
      "id": "6999450c000000000059acfe",
      "text": "[taktamur#69913d720000000000df5f75]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652364,
      "updated": 1771652365
    },
    {
      "id": "699944e5000000000059acf5",
      "text": ">[https://gyazo.com/98835185e7fc82dcc9d3f5e3d307f2c7]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652325,
      "updated": 1771652328
    },
    {
      "id": "699944e7000000000059acf6",
      "text": "> ↑2026/02/15",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652328,
      "updated": 1771652328
    },
    {
      "id": "699944e7000000000059acf7",
      "text": ">  遠目での配色が同じなら、アイコン変更してもバレない仮説[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652328,
      "updated": 1771652328
    },
    {
      "id": "699944e7000000000059acf8",
      "text": ">  [https://gyazo.com/fd0dd50189a88109d322124b10f031a6]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652328,
      "updated": 1771652328
    },
    {
      "id": "699944e7000000000059acf9",
      "text": ">  [https://gyazo.com/638ec51c63378238305938accfae499d]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652328,
      "updated": 1771652328
    },
    {
      "id": "699944e7000000000059acfa",
      "text": ">  何度転生しても抑えきれないクチバシの遺伝子",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771652328,
      "updated": 1771652328
    },
    {
      "id": "6999424100000000008e8437",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771651650,
      "updated": 1771651651
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf8b900000000005dac15",
      "text": "from [2026/02/11]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829434,
      "updated": 1771829434
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf8d200000000004225cb",
      "text": "[nomadoor.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829459,
      "updated": 1771829459
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf8b900000000005dac16",
      "text": " 井戸端メンバーがソシャゲキャラみたいに…(；・∀・)",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829434,
      "updated": 1771829461
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf8b900000000005dac17",
      "text": " 　ガチャとか実装したくなってきた",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829434,
      "updated": 1771829461
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf8b900000000005dac18",
      "text": " 　 [イドバタリアンガチャ][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829434,
      "updated": 1771829461
    },
    {
      "id": "699bfa8800000000003f1289",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829897,
      "updated": 1771829899
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf92e00000000005d4e39",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829550,
      "updated": 1771829550
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf92e00000000005d4e3a",
      "text": " 一晩井戸端離れてたら誰が誰だかわからんくなった",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829550,
      "updated": 1771829550
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf92e00000000005d4e3b",
      "text": " 　みじっこはずっとフグだよ。安心して",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829550,
      "updated": 1771829550
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf92e00000000005d4e3c",
      "text": " 　アイコンは自分を表現したものなので、自分の要素（大抵は自作であること）が一切入ってないアイコンにしようと思うことがそんなにない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829550,
      "updated": 1771829550
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf92e00000000005d4e3d",
      "text": " 　　（一時期マヤちゃんのアイコンにしてたのは除く）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829550,
      "updated": 1771829550
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf92e00000000005d4e3e",
      "text": " いややっぱ誰コイツになって名前確認しちゃうな",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829550,
      "updated": 1771829550
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf92e00000000005d4e3f",
      "text": " 　そしてほんとに知らない人おったけど",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829550,
      "updated": 1771829550
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf92e00000000005d4e40",
      "text": " [AIっぽい自作絵]描いたら混ざれるかな",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829550,
      "updated": 1771829550
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf92e00000000005d4e41",
      "text": " 　ほんとに描いてる人いたけどまあまあむずいと思う",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829550,
      "updated": 1771829550
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf92e00000000005d4e42",
      "text": " 　https://x.com/i/status/2018165916656431422",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829550,
      "updated": 1771829550
    },
    {
      "id": "699bf92e00000000005d4e43",
      "text": " 　まあただそんなことしても[アイデンティティ]の欠片もないのでやらないけど",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771829550,
      "updated": 1771829550
    },
    {
      "id": "699949bc000000000030e64b",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771653566,
      "updated": 1771829467
    },
    {
      "id": "6999435d0000000000a019df",
      "text": "[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771651935,
      "updated": 1771651937
    },
    {
      "id": "6999424300000000008e8438",
      "text": "\t気になったから自分もGeminiにさわやかにしてもらった",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771651651,
      "updated": 1771653456
    },
    {
      "id": "699943830000000000a019e1",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/b44f14376428b039d6aee4c607176c04]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771651973,
      "updated": 1771651981
    },
    {
      "id": "699943950000000000a019e3",
      "text": "\t\t元の絵はそのままに、背景がついて空の色が投影されただけやな…",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771651991,
      "updated": 1771653503
    },
    {
      "id": "69994987000000000030e649",
      "text": "\t\t\t服装と背景が状況的に合っていない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771653513,
      "updated": 1771653549
    },
    {
      "id": "6999499c000000000030e64a",
      "text": "\t\t背景を描いたことがなかったのでまあ参考になる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771653533,
      "updated": 1771653559
    },
    {
      "id": "6999438c0000000000a019e2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771651981,
      "updated": 1771651981
    },
    {
      "id": "6999435a0000000000a019de",
      "text": "あと、[seibe.icon]さん[meganii.icon]さんも変わっているけど、これはどうなの？ [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1771651931,
      "updated": 1771662517
    },
    {
      "id": "6999705d0000000000980ff3",
      "text": " どうなんだろ[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771663453,
      "updated": 1771663460
    },
    {
      "id": "699970650000000000980ff4",
      "text": "  さわやかアイコンかどうか分からず載せてないのでさわやかアイコンだったら教えてほしい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771663461,
      "updated": 1771663503
    },
    {
      "id": "699943620000000000a019e0",
      "text": "\t確かどこかの日記でそういっているのを見たような…[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771651940,
      "updated": 1771671797
    },
    {
      "id": "699990cc0000000000bf890e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771671756,
      "updated": 1771671756
    },
    {
      "id": "699941f000000000008e842e",
      "text": "[さわやかな井戸端]",
